  Text: |-
    This project brings together a collection of commonly used Lens patterns in one place.
    
    Enable one scene object at a time to explore and understand each pattern individually.
    
    Many of these essential patterns are also available in the Asset Library as standalone packages.
    
    The goal of this sample is to showcase them all together in a single, easy-to-navigate experience.
